  "root_text": {
    "sn14.17:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 14.17 ",
    "sn14.17:0.2": "2. Dutiyavagga ",
    "sn14.17:0.3": "Assaddhasaṁsandanasutta ",
    "sn14.17:1.1": "Sāvatthiyaṁ viharati. ",
    "sn14.17:1.2": "“Dhātusova, bhikkhave, sattā saṁsandanti samenti. ",
    "sn14.17:1.3": "Assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:1.4": "ahirikā ahirikehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:1.5": "anottappino anottappīhi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:1.6": "appassutā appassutehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:1.7": "kusītā kusītehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:1.8": "muṭṭhassatino muṭṭhassatīhi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:1.9": "duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti. ",
    "sn14.17:2.1": "Atītampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṁ dhātusova sattā saṁsandiṁsu samiṁsu. ",
    "sn14.17:2.2": "Assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandiṁsu samiṁsu; ",
    "sn14.17:2.3": "ahirikā ahirikehi saddhiṁ saṁsandiṁsu samiṁsu; ",
    "sn14.17:2.4": "anottappino anottappīhi saddhiṁ saṁsandiṁsu samiṁsu; ",
    "sn14.17:2.5": "appassutā appassutehi saddhiṁ saṁsandiṁsu samiṁsu; ",
    "sn14.17:2.6": "kusītā kusītehi saddhiṁ saṁsandiṁsu samiṁsu; ",
    "sn14.17:2.7": "muṭṭhassatino muṭṭhassatīhi saddhiṁ saṁsandiṁsu samiṁsu; ",
    "sn14.17:2.8": "duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṁ saṁsandiṁsu samiṁsu. ",
    "sn14.17:3.1": "Anāgatampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṁ dhātusova sattā saṁsandissanti samessanti. ",
    "sn14.17:3.2": "Assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandissanti samessanti; ",
    "sn14.17:3.3": "ahirikā ahirikehi saddhiṁ saṁsandissanti samessanti; ",
    "sn14.17:3.4": "anottappino anottappīhi saddhiṁ …pe… ",
    "sn14.17:3.5": "appassutā appassutehi saddhiṁ …pe… ",
    "sn14.17:3.6": "kusītā kusītehi saddhiṁ …pe… ",
    "sn14.17:3.7": "muṭṭhassatino muṭṭhassatīhi saddhiṁ …pe… ",
    "sn14.17:3.8": "duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṁ saṁsandissanti samessanti. ",
    "sn14.17:4.1": "Etarahipi kho, bhikkhave, paccuppannaṁ addhānaṁ dhātusova sattā saṁsandanti samenti. ",
    "sn14.17:4.2": "Assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:4.3": "ahirikā ahirikehi saddhiṁ …pe… ",
    "sn14.17:4.4": "anottappino anottappīhi saddhiṁ …pe… ",
    "sn14.17:4.5": "appassutā appassutehi saddhiṁ …pe… ",
    "sn14.17:4.6": "kusītā kusītehi saddhiṁ …pe… ",
    "sn14.17:4.7": "muṭṭhassatino muṭṭhassatīhi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:4.8": "duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti. ",
    "sn14.17:5.1": "Dhātusova, bhikkhave, sattā saṁsandanti samenti. ",
    "sn14.17:5.2": "Saddhā saddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:5.3": "hirimanā hirimanehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:5.4": "ottappino ottappīhi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:5.5": "bahussutā bahussutehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:5.6": "āraddhavīriyā āraddhavīriyehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:5.7": "upaṭṭhitassatino upaṭṭhitassatīhi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.17:5.8": "paññavanto paññavantehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti. ",
    "sn14.17:5.9": "Atītampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṁ …pe… ",
    "sn14.17:5.10": "anāgatampi kho, bhikkhave …pe… ",
    "sn14.17:5.11": "etarahipi kho, bhikkhave, paccuppannaṁ addhānaṁ dhātusova sattā saṁsandanti samenti. ",
    "sn14.17:5.12": "Saddhā saddhehi saddhiṁ …pe… ",
    "sn14.17:5.13": "paññavanto paññavantehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samentī”ti. ",
    "sn14.17:5.14": "Sattamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "sn14.17:0.1": "Linked Discourses 14.17 ",
    "sn14.17:0.2": "Chapter Two ",
    "sn14.17:0.3": "Faithless ",
    "sn14.17:1.1": "At Sāvatthī. ",
    "sn14.17:1.2": "“Mendicants, sentient beings join together and converge because of an element: ",
    "sn14.17:1.3": "the faithless with the faithless, ",
    "sn14.17:1.4": "the unconscientious with the unconscientious, ",
    "sn14.17:1.5": "the imprudent with the imprudent, ",
    "sn14.17:1.6": "the unlearned with the unlearned, ",
    "sn14.17:1.7": "the lazy with the lazy, ",
    "sn14.17:1.8": "the unmindful with the unmindful, ",
    "sn14.17:1.9": "and the witless with the witless. ",
    "sn14.17:2.1": "In the past, too, sentient beings came together and converged because of an element. … ",
    "sn14.17:2.2": "",
    "sn14.17:2.3": "",
    "sn14.17:2.4": "",
    "sn14.17:2.5": "",
    "sn14.17:2.6": "",
    "sn14.17:2.7": "",
    "sn14.17:2.8": "",
    "sn14.17:3.1": "In the future, too, sentient beings will join together and converge because of an element. … ",
    "sn14.17:3.2": "",
    "sn14.17:3.3": "",
    "sn14.17:3.4": "",
    "sn14.17:3.5": "",
    "sn14.17:3.6": "",
    "sn14.17:3.7": "",
    "sn14.17:3.8": "",
    "sn14.17:4.1": "At present, too, sentient beings join together and converge because of an element. … ",
    "sn14.17:4.2": "",
    "sn14.17:4.3": "",
    "sn14.17:4.4": "",
    "sn14.17:4.5": "",
    "sn14.17:4.6": "",
    "sn14.17:4.7": "",
    "sn14.17:4.8": "",
    "sn14.17:5.1": "Sentient beings join together and converge because of an element: ",
    "sn14.17:5.2": "the faithful with the faithful, ",
    "sn14.17:5.3": "the conscientious with the conscientious, ",
    "sn14.17:5.4": "the prudent with the prudent, ",
    "sn14.17:5.5": "the learned with the learned, ",
    "sn14.17:5.6": "the energetic with the energetic, ",
    "sn14.17:5.7": "the mindful with the mindful, ",
    "sn14.17:5.8": "and the wise with the wise. ",
    "sn14.17:5.9": "In the past … ",
    "sn14.17:5.10": "In the future … ",
    "sn14.17:5.11": "At present, too, sentient beings join together and converge because of an element. …” ",
    "sn14.17:5.12": "",
    "sn14.17:5.13": ""
  },
